---
title: Easy Char Siu Beef Noodle Stir-Fry with Crushed Peanuts
description: Time to get saucy tonight. This delicious noodle bowl is chock full of colour and flavour, and our absolute favourite bit is the
crunchy peanut nut topping. Big yes!
